movies.name: The Shawshank Redemption
movies.description: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

movies.name: The Godfather
movies.description: The aging patriarch of an organized crime dynasty transfers control of his clandestine empire to his reluctant son.

movies.name: The Dark Knight
movies.description: When the menace known as the Joker emerges from his mysterious past, he wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham.

movies.name: Pulp Fiction
movies.description: The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, a gangster's wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption.

movies.name: Forrest Gump
movies.description: The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, the Vietnam War, the Watergate scandal and other historical events unfold from the perspective of an Alabama man.

movies.name: Inception
movies.description: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a CEO.

movies.name: The Matrix
movies.description: A computer hacker learns from mysterious rebels about the true nature of his reality and his role in the war against its controllers.

movies.name: Interstellar
movies.description: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

movies.name: Summer Wars
movies.description: A math whiz who accidentally causes a collision between a parallel world and Earth.

movies.name: Millennium Actress
movies.description: A TV interviewer and his cameraman who meet a reclusive former actress and travel through her memories and career.

movies.name: Perfect Blue
movies.description: A Japanese singer who leaves her J-pop group to become an actress, and the consequences of her decision.

movies.name: Paprika
movies.description: A scientist who uses her dream alter ego to stop a thief from misusing a device that allows people to enter dreams.

movies.name: A Silent Voice
movies.description: A boy who tries to make amends for bullying a deaf girl in elementary school.

movies.name: Your Name
movies.description: Two high school students who mysteriously start swapping bodies.

movies.name: Wolf Children
movies.description: A woman who falls in love with a half-wolf, half-human man and raises their two children as they grow up.

movies.name: Spirited Away
movies.description: A 10-year-old girl named Chihiro who accidentally discovers a world of spirits and demons while moving to the suburbs with her family.
